OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FIt will be a dry day with some
OL,6,Foccasional cloud but still plenty of
OL,7,Flong sunny spells on offer. Becoming
OL,8,Fvery warm by afternoon, especially in
OL,9,Fthe east.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FIt will be a dry evening with
OL,12,Flargely clear skies and evening
OL,13,Fsunshine to start but turning
OL,14,Fcloudier. Dry and mostly cloudy
OL,15,Fovernight with some clear intervals.
OL,16,
OL,17,CWednesday:FAnother dry day with
OL,18,Fvariable cloud but still plenty of
OL,19,Flong sunny spells. The best of the
OL,20,Fsunshine in the west with the east
OL,21,Fcloudier. Feeling warm in the sunshine.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
