OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,6,FMostly dry on Thursday with sunny
OL,7,Fspells. Then becoming mostly cloudy on
OL,8,FFriday with a little light rain
OL,9,Fpossible. Cloudy with rain, perhaps
OL,10,Fheavy, spreading eastwards on Saturday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
